gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 111, Raptors 96
gameRecap.excerpt: Orlando defeats Toronto, 111-96. For Orlando, Paolo Banchero led the way with 26 points, six rebounds, and five assists while aided by Franz Wagner (22 points, nine rebounds, five assists) in the victory. Jordan Nwora finished with 18 points and seven rebounds with Gary Trent Jr. adding 15 points, five rebounds, and two steals for Toronto in the losing effort. Orlando improves to 40-28, while Toronto moves to 23-45 in the loss.
